<h2>
    <a href="/blog/diffusion-on-the-surface-of-a-torus/">Diffusion on the surface of a torus</a>
</h2>




<h6 class="post-meta">
    Posted by:
    
    <a href="/blog/author/christian/">christian</a>
    
    
    
    in
    
    <a href="/blog/category/featured-on-frontpage/">Featured on frontpage</a>
    
    
    
    on 27 Dec 2018
</h6>





<a href="/blog/diffusion-on-the-surface-of-a-torus/">
    <img class="img-thumbnail pull-left" src="/static/media/uploads/blog/torus/.thumbnails/cropped-torus-500.png/cropped-torus-500-90x90.png">
</a>





<p><a href="/book/chapter-7-matplotlib/examples/the-two-dimensional-diffusion-equation/">An example in Chapter 7 of the scipython book</a> describes the numerical solution of the two-dimensional heat equation for a flat plate with edges held at a fixed temperature.</p>




