    <a href="/blog/author/christian/">christian</a>
    
    
    
    in
    
    <a href="/blog/category/featured-on-frontpage/">Featured on frontpage</a>
    
    
    
    on 30 Nov 2018
</h6>





<a href="/blog/depicting-a-torus-as-an-svg-image/">
    <img class="img-thumbnail pull-left" src="/static/media/uploads/blog/torus/.thumbnails/pastel-torus.png/pastel-torus-90x90.png">
</a>





<p>SVG may not be the most obvious choice for depicting a 3-D object, but with some care over the perspective and ordering of the plotted points, it can be done.</p>




